  "response": "After upgrading your Town Hall to level 6 in Clash of Clans, here are some recommended steps:\n\n1. Upgrade Defenses\n- Upgrade new defensive buildings available at TH6\n- Focus on air defense and wizard towers\n- Improve existing defenses like walls and archer towers\n\n2. Army Composition\n- Unlock new troops like Balloons and Dragons\n- Upgrade existing troops\n- Start learning advanced attack strategies\n\n3. Resource Management\n- Upgrade collectors and storage\n- Build more resource buildings\n- Focus on protecting your resources\n\n4. Lab Upgrades\n- Prioritize troop and spell upgrades\n- Research new troops available at TH6\n\n5. Builder Base\n- Continue developing your Builder Base\n- Upgrade buildings and troops there\n\n6. Clan Castle\n- Request and donate troops\n- Participate in Clan Wars\n\n7. Heroes\n- Start saving for Barbarian King when possible\n- Keep heroes upgrading consistently\n\n8. Storages and Economy\n- Upgrade resource storages\n- Balance gold and elixir upgrades\n\n9. Additional Buildings\n- Add new Army Camps\n- Build extra resource buildings\n\n10. Plan Next Upgrades\n- Create a strategic upgrade priority list\n- Balance offensive and defensive improvements\n\nRemember to stay active, strategic, and enjoy the game!",
